{"tid":1706311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工","createTime":"2019-11-11T05:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T05:36:07.000Z","uid":24173,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec0010e717a30e6c8c06f709f050cd9620622f0","tid":1706311,"uid":24173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工<br />\n如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工<br />\n如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工<br />\n如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果香港會嬴 我寧願無左份工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人比D志氣好唔好阿<br />\n<br />\n今日仲講願意&quot;被罷工&quot;嘅人,而唔願意去罷工嘅人, 中槍位手足係你地害咖, 你地唔罷,仲要人地幫你罷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地全部人都差佢一槍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然上次講過, 不過再講一次, 今日開始唔會再係連登係開POST"},{"pid":"c57886235c8f4fbcfca38cac730f84105a1c6fc8","tid":1706311,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:09:25.000Z","msg":"引狗無差別襲擊準時返工打工仔，以後無人返工了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703964</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84b98d6fe0d05b9dfd4eeb560c301b3d85ecc9c2","tid":1706311,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"人一生，需要嘅一個床位，三餐溫飽。<br />\n<br />\n只要肯做，一定搵到食。<br />\n<br />\n工無咗，再搵，自由民主同香港無咗，就搵唔返。"},{"pid":"f582bd9116ec6473320b9000c78195a578630964","tid":1706311,"uid":24173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:13:40.000Z","msg":"今日仲係手足中槍之後 仲要大大聲講被罷工嘅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地全部人都有份開呢一槍</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我就係咁小學雞"},{"pid":"ee2efe7842505251c0c0865d47156618fc0f3558","tid":1706311,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T05:15:19.000Z","msg":"無份工唔緊要<br />\n我地贏到就得"},{"pid":"3d94eabd7d548636248244590939051adeca6772","tid":1706311,"uid":45518,"